---
// src/components/sections/Features.astro
---

<section class="features">
  <div class="container features__grid">

    <!-- Card 1: WhatsApp Registration -->
    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-icon feat-icon--green">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feat-title">Registro fácil por WhatsApp</h3>
      <p class="feat-desc">
        Anota tus gastos e ingresos con un mensaje, una nota de voz, o una foto
        de tu factura. Pablo lo entiende y registra todo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2: Visual Reports -->
    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-icon feat-icon--amber">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2B2C64" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feat-title">Reportes visuales de gastos</h3>
      <p class="feat-desc">
        Entiende qué sucede con tu dinero con gráficas y balances simples.
        Detecta tus gastos hormiga al instante.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3: Reminders -->
    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-icon feat-icon--navy">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feat-title">Recordatorios amigables</h3>
      <p class="feat-desc">
        Pablo te envía recordatorios motivadores (no regaños) para que
        ahorres y tengas siempre el control de tu dinero.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 4: Tips & Goals -->
    <div class="feat-card">
      <div class="feat-icon feat-icon--purple">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="9" y1="18" x2="15" y2="18"/><line x1="10" y1="22" x2="14" y2="22"/><path d="M15.09 14c.18-.98.65-1.74 1.41-2.5A4.65 4.65 0 0 0 18 8 6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1.45.57 2.75 1.5 3.75.74.76 1.22 1.52 1.41 2.25"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="feat-title">Tips y metas financieras</h3>
      <p class="feat-desc">
        Define objetivos (ej. "ahorrar para un viaje"). Pablo te anima y
        comparte tips personalizados para ahorrar y alcanzar tus metas.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background: var(--bg-how);
    padding: 0 0 var(--section-py);
  }

  .features__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .feat-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .feat-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .feat-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feat-icon--green  { background: #3FA643; }
  .feat-icon--amber  { background: #FCAA1F; }
  .feat-icon--navy   { background: #2B2C64; }
  .feat-icon--purple { background: #5A4FCF; }

  .feat-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-heading);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .feat-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-body);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feat-card {
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
